data.title: MARC Code List for Geographic Areas: Name Sequence (Library of Congress)
data.meta_description: The MARC Code List for Geographic Areas consists of a list of geographic areas and their associated one to seven-character codes.  The list includes separate codes for countries, first order political divisions of some countries, regions, geographic features, outre space, and celestial bodies.
